{"tid":2406913,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"兩張圖看完如何分辨麥高植(麥高植(麥高植))與蘭度夫(蘭度夫(蘭度夫))","createTime":"2021-02-13T14:48:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T20:26:32.000Z","uid":38189,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"20b078b5426a19b0ccb7bc418071513362ffb177","tid":2406913,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T14:48:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YzQ4LRO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYzQ4LRO.jpg&h=4bbaeac5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sz1zoDu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSz1zoDu.jpg&h=5a5ca222&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 麥高植髮質比蘭度夫幼和飄逸。<br />\n<br />\n2. 麥高植眉毛比蘭度夫濃。<br />\n<br />\n3. 麥高植眼睛比蘭度夫大，雙眼皮較明顯。<br />\n<br />\n4. 蘭度夫鼻翼比麥高植闊。<br />\n<br />\n5. 蘭度夫顴骨比麥高植突出。<br />\n<br />\n6. 麥高植臉形較短闊，蘭度夫臉形較窄長。<br />\n<br />\n7. 蘭度夫散發秀氣，麥高植散發陽剛味。"},{"pid":"7d7ae6d64ab291b64055f6982cb6561eb824e304","tid":2406913,"uid":222390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T14:48:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf59efd39e577589b3c53205ae58918c18b3f37","tid":2406913,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T14:49:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac3c08fb8f904762c50f2c81f6967b0a352b0f2","tid":2406913,"uid":379666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T14:49:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />))"},{"pid":"77be1ff8c468cffaff5a1abf80a8b3ada9afaebd","tid":2406913,"uid":36238,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"